	<Title>
		Acute sinusitis: Do over-the-counter treatments help?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Over-the-counter drugs may provide some relief from the symptoms of acute sinusitis.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		I have acute sinusitis, and my doctor doesn&apos;t think I need antibiotics. Are there nonprescription medications that can help relieve symptoms?
	</Question>
